Spain’s Gomez Says Interns Will Contribute to Social Security

-- B y   M a n u e l   B a i g o r r i
-- 
2011-10-21T12:00:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/spain-s-gomez-says-interns-will-contribute-to-social-security.html
Spain ’s Labor Minister Valeriano
Gomez said interns will now contribute to the Spanish social
security to “avoid any sort of abuse” of this category of
workers. Gomez, speaking at a press conference in  Madrid  today,
said about 30,000 young interns will now contribute to the
social security system.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Manuel Baigorri at 
 mbaigorri@bloomberg.net  